       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    COI84900.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA COI84900.                                         *
      *                                                                *
      *     Browse Despesas                                            *
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE COI84900         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD6702 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD3606 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY COCV8490.
       COPY COCV8491.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY COCK0001.
       COPY COCK0002.
       COPY ETCL0002.
       COPY ARCL0039.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            SWITCH
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  SW-SWITCH.
           05 SW-CURSOR                  PIC X(01) VALUE SPACES.
              88 SW-CURSOR-NONE                    VALUE '0'.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-COVT6702 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT6702'.
           05 CON-COVT3606 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT3606'.
           05 CON-DSP      PIC X(03) VALUE 'DSP'.
           05 CON-S        PIC X(01) VALUE 'S'.
           05 CON-ESPACOS  PIC X(01) VALUE ' '.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            PROGRAM CONTROL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-PROGRAM-CONTROL.
           05 WS-TEM-PROJ         PIC X(01) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-PROGNAME         PIC X(08) VALUE 'COI84900'.
           05 WS-DATA-MIN         PIC X(10) VALUE '0001-01-01'.
           05 WS-DATA-MAX         PIC X(10) VALUE '9999-12-31'.
           05 WS-GREFINV          PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-GREFINV-MIN      PIC X(12) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-GREFINV-MAX      PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-NIDPROJECTO-MIN  PIC X(08) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-NIDPROJECTO-MAX  PIC X(08) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-CSTATUS-MIN      PIC X(02) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-CSTATUS-MAX      PIC X(02) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-GCLIENTE-MIN     PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-GCLIENTE-MAX     PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-DDATAEMIS2-MIN   PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-DDATAEMIS2-MAX   PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-DDATDUE          PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 WS-DDATDUEUNTIL     PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
**AF       05 WS-INDEX            PIC 9(02) VALUE ZEROES.

      *--- Chave para documentos (NIDPROJECTO, NIDINVOICE)
           05 WS-CCHAVE.
              10 WS-CCHAVE-01      PIC X(08).
              10 WS-CCHAVE-02      PIC X(10).
              10 FILLER REDEFINES WS-CCHAVE-02.
                 15 WS-CCHAVE-02-9 PIC 9(10).

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *              DECLARACOES DE CURSORES DB2                     *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CURSOR-VARS.
           05 FILLER                     PIC X(01) VALUE SPACES.

           EXEC SQL
                DECLARE CURCOT02 CURSOR FOR
                 SELECT
                       NIDINVOICE
                     , NIDPROJECTO
                     , GCLIENTE
                     , DDATAINSER
                     , DDATAEMISS
                     , DDATAEMIS2
                     , DDATEDUE
                     , CPRAZO
                     , NTOTALAMOUNT
                     , NTAXAMOUNT
                     , GDESCINVOICE
                     , CSTATUS
                     , CUSERID
                     , HTIMEST
                     , GREFINV
                     , DPAG
                     , CTIPDOC
                     , CMOEDA
                     , CIMPOSTO
                     , NOTAS
                     , NTOTCTRV
                     , NTAXCTRV
                     , CTIPFAC
                     , NTOTPAG
                     , NTAXPAG
                     , NTOTRET
                     , NTAXRET
                     , CIBAN
                     , MVOR
                     , MVORCTRV
                     , PROJDSP
                 FROM COVT6702_EXPENSES
**AF  *          WHERE  (GREFINV     >= :WS-GREFINV-MIN
**AF  *             AND  GREFINV     <= :WS-GREFINV-MAX
**AF             WHERE  (GREFINV   LIKE :WS-GREFINV-MIN

                    AND  NIDPROJECTO >= :WS-NIDPROJECTO-MIN
                    AND  NIDPROJECTO <= :WS-NIDPROJECTO-MAX
                    AND  CSTATUS     >= :WS-CSTATUS-MIN
                    AND  CSTATUS     <= :WS-CSTATUS-MAX
                    AND  GCLIENTE    >= :WS-GCLIENTE-MIN
                    AND  GCLIENTE    <= :WS-GCLIENTE-MAX
                    AND  DDATEDUE    >= :WS-DDATDUE
                    AND  DDATEDUE    <= :WS-DDATDUEUNTIL  )

                    AND (NIDPROJECTO >  :COCD6702-NIDPROJECTO

                     OR (NIDPROJECTO  = :COCD6702-NIDPROJECTO
                    AND  NIDINVOICE  >= :COCD6702-NIDINVOICE))

                  ORDER  BY NIDPROJECTO,
                         NIDINVOICE
           END-EXEC.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE COI84900         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0004.

           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.

           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO COCV8490-MSG.
           MOVE COCV8490-ASE               TO COCV8491-ASE.

           MOVE ZEROES                     TO COCV8491-INDICE.
           PERFORM 1100-LIMPA-OCCURS
              THRU 1199-LIMPA-OCCURS-EXIT
             UNTIL COCV8491-PAGINA-CHEIA.

       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1100-LIMPA-OCCURS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1100-LIMPA-OCCURS.

           ADD 1                       TO COCV8491-INDICE.

           MOVE ZEROES TO   COCV8491-D-NIDINVOICE(COCV8491-INDICE)
                            COCV8491-D-MVOR(COCV8491-INDICE)
                            COCV8491-D-NTOTALAMOUNT(COCV8491-INDICE)
                            COCV8491-D-NTAXAMOUNT(COCV8491-INDICE)
                            COCV8491-D-NVALTOT(COCV8491-INDICE)

           MOVE SPACES TO   COCV8491-D-NIDPROJECTO(COCV8491-INDICE)
                            COCV8491-D-GCLIENTE(COCV8491-INDICE)
                            COCV8491-D-GREFINV(COCV8491-INDICE)
                            COCV8491-D-CPRAZO(COCV8491-INDICE)
                            COCV8491-D-CSTATUS(COCV8491-INDICE)
                            COCV8491-D-CIMPOSTO(COCV8491-INDICE)
                            COCV8491-D-CMOEDA(COCV8491-INDICE)
                            COCV8491-D-PROJDSP(COCV8491-INDICE)

           MOVE VIAK0002-DATA-MINIMA TO
                            COCV8491-D-DDATAINSER(COCV8491-INDICE)
                            COCV8491-D-DDATAEMISS(COCV8491-INDICE)
                            COCV8491-D-DDATAEMIS2(COCV8491-INDICE)
                            COCV8491-D-DDATEDUE(COCV8491-INDICE)
                            COCV8491-D-DDATEPAG(COCV8491-INDICE).

       1199-LIMPA-OCCURS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV8490-CLIENTE      TO COCV8491-CLIENTE.
           MOVE COCV8490-NIDINVOICE   TO COCV8491-NIDINVOICE.
           MOVE COCV8490-NIDPROJECTO  TO COCV8491-NIDPROJECTO.
           MOVE COCV8490-GREFINV      TO COCV8491-GREFINV.
           MOVE COCV8490-CSTATUS      TO COCV8491-CSTATUS.
           MOVE COCV8490-GCLIENTE     TO COCV8491-GCLIENTE.
           MOVE COCV8490-DDATDUE      TO WS-DDATDUE         .
           MOVE WS-DDATDUE            TO COCV8491-DDATDUE   .
           MOVE COCV8490-DDATDUEUNTIL TO WS-DDATDUEUNTIL    .
           MOVE WS-DDATDUEUNTIL       TO COCV8491-DDATDUEUNTIL.
           MOVE COCV8490-NIDINVOICEP  TO COCV8491-NIDINVOICEP.
           MOVE COCV8490-NIDPROJECTOP TO COCV8491-NIDPROJECTOP.

           PERFORM 2010-VALIDACOES
              THRU 2019-VALIDACOES-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2020-OPEN
                 THRU 2029-OPEN-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2030-FETCH
                 THRU 2039-FETCH-EXIT



              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 IF DB2-OK
                    PERFORM 2040-CONTINUA
                       THRU 2049-CONTINUA-EXIT
                 ELSE
                    COMPUTE COCV8491-DIMINUI-LENGTH EQUAL
                         COCV8491-INDICE-INVERSO * COCV8491-LENGTH-OCCUR
                    COMPUTE COCV8491-LENGTH EQUAL COCV8491-LENGTH
                         - COCV8491-DIMINUI-LENGTH
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO COCV8491-NIDINVOICE-S
                    MOVE COCK0001-NIDINVOICE-N-EXISTS
                      TO COCV8491-NIDINVOICE-MSG
                    MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                      TO COCV8491-NIDINVOICE-CAPLIC
                 END-IF
              END-IF
              PERFORM 2070-CLOSE
                 THRU 2079-CLOSE-EXIT
           END-IF.






       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2010-VALIDACOES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2010-VALIDACOES.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2010-VALIDACOES' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF COCV8490-NIDPROJECTO NOT EQUAL SPACES
             MOVE COCV8490-NIDPROJECTO TO WS-NIDPROJECTO-MIN
                                          WS-NIDPROJECTO-MAX
           ELSE
             MOVE ALL ' '              TO WS-NIDPROJECTO-MIN
             MOVE ALL '9'              TO WS-NIDPROJECTO-MAX
**AF         MOVE X'00'
**AF                                   TO WS-NIDPROJECTO-MIN
**AF         MOVE HIGH-VALUES          TO WS-NIDPROJECTO-MAX
           END-IF.

           IF COCV8490-GREFINV     NOT EQUAL SPACES
**AF  *      MOVE COCV8490-GREFINV     TO WS-GREFINV-MIN
**AF  *                                   WS-GREFINV-MAX
**AF         MOVE  '%'                 TO WS-GREFINV-MIN(1:1)
**AF
**AF         PERFORM VARYING WS-INDEX FROM 10 BY -1
**AF           UNTIL WS-INDEX = 1
**AF              OR COCV8490-GREFINV(WS-INDEX:1) NOT = ' '
**AF             CONTINUE
**AF         END-PERFORM
**AF
**AF         ADD 1                     TO WS-INDEX
**AF         MOVE  COCV8490-GREFINV    TO WS-GREFINV-MIN(2:WS-INDEX)
**AF         ADD 1                     TO WS-INDEX
**AF  *      IF WS-INDEX > 10
**AF  *         MOVE 10                TO WS-INDEX
**AF  *      END-IF
**AF         MOVE  ALL '%'             TO WS-GREFINV-MIN(WS-INDEX: )
**AF  *      DISPLAY 'WS-GREFINV-MIN: ' WS-GREFINV-MIN
**AF  *      CALL 'XXXXXX'
           ELSE
**AF  *      MOVE ALL ' '              TO WS-GREFINV-MIN
**AF  *      MOVE ALL '9'              TO WS-GREFINV-MAX
**AF         MOVE ALL '%'              TO WS-GREFINV-MIN
           END-IF.

           IF COCV8490-CSTATUS     NOT EQUAL SPACES
             MOVE COCV8490-CSTATUS     TO WS-CSTATUS-MIN
                                          WS-CSTATUS-MAX
           ELSE
             MOVE ALL ' '              TO WS-CSTATUS-MIN
             MOVE ALL '9'              TO WS-CSTATUS-MAX
           END-IF.

           IF COCV8490-GCLIENTE    NOT EQUAL SPACES
             MOVE COCV8490-GCLIENTE    TO WS-GCLIENTE-MIN
                                          WS-GCLIENTE-MAX
           ELSE
             MOVE ALL ' '              TO WS-GCLIENTE-MIN
             MOVE ALL '9'              TO WS-GCLIENTE-MAX
           END-IF.

      *    IF COCV8490-DDATAEMIS2      EQUAL SPACES
      *    OR COCV8490-DDATAEMIS2      EQUAL WS-DATA-MIN
      *      MOVE WS-DATA-MIN          TO WS-DDATAEMIS2-MIN
      *      MOVE WS-DATA-MAX          TO WS-DDATAEMIS2-MAX
      *    ELSE
      *      MOVE COCV8490-DDATAEMIS2  TO WS-DDATAEMIS2-MIN
      *      MOVE WS-DATA-MAX          TO WS-DDATAEMIS2-MAX
      *    END-IF.
           MOVE COCV8490-DDATDUE       TO WS-DDATAEMIS2-MIN
           MOVE COCV8490-DDATDUEUNTIL  TO WS-DDATAEMIS2-MAX

           MOVE COCV8490-NIDINVOICEP   TO COCD6702-NIDINVOICE.
           MOVE COCV8490-NIDPROJECTOP  TO COCD6702-NIDPROJECTO.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2010-VALIDACOES-EXIT'  TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2019-VALIDACOES-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2020-OPEN
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2020-OPEN.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2020-OPEN' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
               OPEN CURCOT02
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-COVT6702               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           IF VIAL0015-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2020-OPEN   ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE ' WS-GREFINV-MIN '      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  WS-GREFINV-MIN         TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.


           IF VIAL0015-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2020-OPEN   ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE ' WS-GREFINV-MAX     '  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  WS-GREFINV-MAX         TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.


           IF VIAL0015-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2020-OPEN   ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'WS-NIDPROJECTO-MIN  '  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE WS-NIDPROJECTO-MIN      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.


           IF VIAL0015-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2020-OPEN   ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'WS-NIDPROJECTO-MAX  '  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE WS-NIDPROJECTO-MAX      TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.



           IF VIAL0015-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2020-OPEN   ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'WS-CSTATUS-MIN      '  TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  WS-CSTATUS-MIN         TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.


           IF VIAL0015-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2020-OPEN   ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'WS-CSTATUS-MAX       ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  WS-CSTATUS-MAX         TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.


           IF VIAL0015-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2020-OPEN   ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'WS-GCLIENTE-MIN      ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  WS-GCLIENTE-MIN        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.



           IF VIAL0015-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2020-OPEN   ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'WS-GCLIENTE-MAX      ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  WS-GCLIENTE-MAX        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.


           IF VIAL0015-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2020-OPEN   ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'WS-DDATDUE           ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  WS-DDATDUE             TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.


           IF VIAL0015-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2020-OPEN   ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'WS-DDATDUEUNTIL      ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  WS-DDATDUEUNTIL        TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.


           IF VIAL0015-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2020-OPEN   ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'COCD6702-NIDPROJECTO ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  COCD6702-NIDPROJECTO   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.


           IF VIAL0015-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2020-OPEN   ' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'COCD6702-NIDINVOICE  ' TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  COCD6702-NIDINVOICE    TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.







           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

       2029-OPEN-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2030-FETCH
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2030-FETCH.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2030-FETCH' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
              FETCH CURCOT02
               INTO
                   :COCD6702-NIDINVOICE
                 , :COCD6702-NIDPROJECTO
                 , :COCD6702-GCLIENTE
                 , :COCD6702-DDATAINSER
                 , :COCD6702-DDATAEMISS
                 , :COCD6702-DDATAEMIS2
                 , :COCD6702-DDATEDUE
                 , :COCD6702-CPRAZO
                 , :COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT
                 , :COCD6702-NTAXAMOUNT
                 , :COCD6702-GDESCINVOICE
                 , :COCD6702-CSTATUS
                 , :COCD6702-CUSERID
                 , :COCD6702-HTIMEST
                 , :COCD6702-GREFINV
                 , :COCD6702-DPAG
                 , :COCD6702-CTIPDOC
                 , :COCD6702-CMOEDA
                 , :COCD6702-CIMPOSTO
                 , :COCD6702-NOTAS
                 , :COCD6702-NTOTCTRV
                 , :COCD6702-NTAXCTRV
                 , :COCD6702-CTIPFAC
                 , :COCD6702-NTOTPAG
                 , :COCD6702-NTAXPAG
                 , :COCD6702-NTOTRET
                 , :COCD6702-NTAXRET
                 , :COCD6702-CIBAN
                 , :COCD6702-MVOR
                 , :COCD6702-MVORCTRV
                 , :COCD6702-PROJDSP
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT6702               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

       2039-FETCH-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                       2040-CONTINUA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2040-CONTINUA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2040-CONTINUA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE ZEROES                     TO COCV8491-INDICE.
           PERFORM 2050-TRATA-OCCURS
              THRU 2059-TRATA-OCCURS-EXIT
      *      UNTIL DB2-NOTFND
             UNTIL NOT DB2-OK
                OR COCV8491-PAGINA-CHEIA
                OR NOT VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF NOT COCV8491-PAGINA-CHEIA
                    COMPUTE COCV8491-INDICE-INVERSO EQUAL
                         COCV8491-INDICE-INVERSO - COCV8491-INDICE
                    COMPUTE COCV8491-DIMINUI-LENGTH EQUAL
                         COCV8491-INDICE-INVERSO * COCV8491-LENGTH-OCCUR
                    COMPUTE COCV8491-LENGTH EQUAL COCV8491-LENGTH -
                         COCV8491-DIMINUI-LENGTH
                    SET  VIAL0002-FIM-CONSULTA TO TRUE
              END-IF
              IF DB2-NOTFND
                    SET  VIAL0002-FIM-CONSULTA TO TRUE
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2049-CONTINUA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2050-TRATA-OCCURS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2050-TRATA-OCCURS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2050-TRATA-OCCURS' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
      *--- Lę COT36_PROJECTS para ver se tem o CLIENTE(Empresa) pedido.
      *--- Se for diferente despreza o registo.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2090-VER-PROJECTO
                 THRU 2090-VER-PROJECTO-EXIT
              IF WS-TEM-PROJ NOT = CON-S
                 CONTINUE
              ELSE
                 ADD 1 TO COCV8491-INDICE
                 MOVE COCD6702-GREFINV
                   TO COCV8491-D-GREFINV(COCV8491-INDICE)
                 MOVE COCD6702-NIDINVOICE
                   TO COCV8491-D-NIDINVOICE(COCV8491-INDICE)
                 MOVE COCD6702-NIDPROJECTO
                   TO COCV8491-D-NIDPROJECTO(COCV8491-INDICE)
                 MOVE COCD6702-GCLIENTE
                   TO COCV8491-D-GCLIENTE(COCV8491-INDICE)
                 MOVE COCD6702-DDATAINSER
                   TO COCV8491-D-DDATAINSER(COCV8491-INDICE)
                 MOVE COCD6702-DDATAEMISS
                   TO COCV8491-D-DDATAEMISS(COCV8491-INDICE)
                 MOVE COCD6702-DDATAEMIS2
                   TO COCV8491-D-DDATAEMIS2(COCV8491-INDICE)
                 MOVE COCD6702-DDATEDUE
                   TO COCV8491-D-DDATEDUE(COCV8491-INDICE)
                 MOVE COCD6702-DPAG
                   TO COCV8491-D-DDATEPAG(COCV8491-INDICE)
                 MOVE COCD6702-CPRAZO
                   TO COCV8491-D-CPRAZO(COCV8491-INDICE)
                 MOVE COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT
                   TO COCV8491-D-NTOTALAMOUNT(COCV8491-INDICE)
                 MOVE COCD6702-MVOR
                   TO COCV8491-D-MVOR(COCV8491-INDICE)
                 MOVE COCD6702-NTAXAMOUNT
                   TO COCV8491-D-NTAXAMOUNT(COCV8491-INDICE)
                 MOVE COCD6702-CSTATUS
                   TO COCV8491-D-CSTATUS(COCV8491-INDICE)
                 MOVE COCD6702-CMOEDA
                   TO COCV8491-D-CMOEDA(COCV8491-INDICE)
                 MOVE COCD6702-CIMPOSTO
                   TO COCV8491-D-CIMPOSTO(COCV8491-INDICE)
                 MOVE COCD6702-PROJDSP
                   TO COCV8491-D-PROJDSP(COCV8491-INDICE)

                 MOVE COCD6702-NTOTPAG
                   TO COCV8491-D-NVALREC (COCV8491-INDICE)
                 MOVE COCD6702-NTAXPAG
                   TO COCV8491-D-NTAXREC (COCV8491-INDICE)

                 COMPUTE COCV8491-D-NVALTOT(COCV8491-INDICE) =
                         COCD6702-NTOTALAMOUNT +
                         COCD6702-NTAXAMOUNT

                 COMPUTE COCV8491-D-NVALLIQ(COCV8491-INDICE)  =
                         COCV8491-D-NVALTOT(COCV8491-INDICE)  -
                        (COCD6702-NTOTPAG + COCD6702-NTAXPAG) -
                        (COCD6702-NTOTRET + COCD6702-NTAXRET)

                 MOVE CON-DSP
                   TO COCV8491-D-CFAMCON(COCV8491-INDICE)
                 MOVE COCD6702-NIDPROJECTO
                   TO WS-CCHAVE-01
                 MOVE COCD6702-NIDINVOICE
                   TO WS-CCHAVE-02-9
                 MOVE WS-CCHAVE
                   TO COCV8491-D-CCHAVE(COCV8491-INDICE)
              END-IF
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 2030-FETCH
              THRU 2039-FETCH-EXIT.

       2059-TRATA-OCCURS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2090-VER-PROJECTO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2090-VER-PROJECTO.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2090-VER-PROJECTO' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCD6702-NIDPROJECTO  TO COCD3606-NIDPROJECTO.

           EXEC SQL
                 SELECT CLIENTE
                  INTO :COCD3606-CLIENTE
                  FROM  COVT3606_PROJECTS
                 WHERE  NIDPROJECTO = :COCD3606-NIDPROJECTO
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT3606 TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 IF COCD3606-CLIENTE = COCV8490-CLIENTE
                    MOVE CON-S TO WS-TEM-PROJ
                 ELSE
                    MOVE CON-ESPACOS TO WS-TEM-PROJ
                 END-IF
              ELSE
                 MOVE CON-ESPACOS TO WS-TEM-PROJ
              END-IF
           ELSE
              MOVE CON-ESPACOS TO WS-TEM-PROJ
           END-IF.

       2090-VER-PROJECTO-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2070-CLOSE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2070-CLOSE.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2070-CLOSE' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EXEC SQL
               CLOSE CURCOT02
           END-EXEC.

       2079-CLOSE-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF COCV8490-NMAXLIST EQUAL ZEROES
              MOVE VIAL0001-CAPLIC         TO ARCL0039-CAPLIC
              MOVE VIAL0001-COPCAO         TO ARCL0039-COPCAO
              PERFORM ARCR0039-NMAXLIST
                 THRU ARCR0039-NMAXLIST-EXIT

              IF ETCL0002-ABEND-DB2
                 MOVE ETCL0002-TABLE-NAME  TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME
                 MOVE ETCL0002-SQLCA       TO VIAL0002-SQLCA
              END-IF

              MOVE ARCL0039-NMAXLIST       TO COCV8491-NMAXLIST
           ELSE
              MOVE COCV8490-NMAXLIST       TO COCV8491-NMAXLIST
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV8491-MSG       TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE COCV8491-LENGTH    TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE COCV8491-NR-CAMPOS TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE COCV8491-INDICE    TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *==============================================================
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
           COPY VIAP0016.
           COPY ARCR0039.
